@startuml
title Azure Real-Time Fraud Detection Platform - Component Diagram\n(Deployment & Performance Architecture)

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor #E1F5FF
    BorderColor #0078D4
    ArrowColor #0078D4
}

skinparam database {
    BackgroundColor #C8E6C9
    BorderColor #388E3C
}

skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FFF9C4
    BorderColor #FBC02D
}

package "Data Ingestion Layer" {
    component [Event Generator] as EventGen <<Simulator>>
    component [Azure Event Hub] as EventHub <<Message Broker>>

    note right of EventHub
        Performance Features:
        - High throughput ingestion
        - Horizontal scaling
        - Event buffering
    end note
}

package "Stream Processing Layer" {
    component [Azure Stream Analytics] as StreamAnalytics <<Stream Processor>>

    note right of StreamAnalytics
        Performance Features:
        - Real-time processing
        - Low-latency analytics
        - Parallel processing
    end note
}

package "Machine Learning Layer" {
    component [Azure ML Service] as AzureML <<ML Platform>>
    component [ML Model] as MLModel <<Trained Model>>
    component [Conda Environment] as CondaEnv <<Runtime>>
    component [Scoring Script] as ScoringScript <<Inference>>

    AzureML ..> MLModel : trains/deploys
    AzureML ..> CondaEnv : manages
    AzureML ..> ScoringScript : deploys

    note right of AzureML
        Deployment:
        - Model versioning
        - A/B testing support
        - Scalable inference
    end note
}

package "Function Orchestration Layer" {
    component [Orchestration Function] as OrchFunction <<Azure Function>>
    component [Benford's Law Function] as BenfordFunction <<Azure Function>>
    component [Fraud Ring Detection Function] as FraudRingFunction <<Azure Function>>

    note right of OrchFunction
        Performance:
        - Serverless scaling
        - Event-driven execution
        - Parallel processing
    end note
}

package "Data Storage Layer" {
    database [Cosmos DB SQL API] as CosmosSQL <<Document Store>>
    database [Cosmos DB Gremlin API] as CosmosGremlin <<Graph Database>>
    database [Azure Synapse Analytics] as Synapse <<Data Warehouse>>

    note right of CosmosSQL
        Performance:
        - Multi-region replication
        - Low-latency reads/writes
        - Automatic indexing
    end note

    note right of CosmosGremlin
        Performance:
        - Graph traversal optimization
        - Horizontal partitioning
        - Global distribution
    end note

    note right of Synapse
        Performance:
        - Massive parallel processing
        - Column-store indexes
        - Result set caching
    end note
}

package "Configuration & Deployment" {
    component [ARM Templates] as ARMTemplate <<IaC>>
    component [Jupyter Notebooks] as Notebooks <<Development>>
    component [Config Files] as Config <<Configuration>>

    note right of ARMTemplate
        Deployment:
        - Infrastructure as Code
        - Repeatable deployments
        - Environment consistency
    end note
}

EventGen --> EventHub : generates\ntransactions
EventHub --> StreamAnalytics : streams events
StreamAnalytics --> MLModel : requests\nfraud score
MLModel --> StreamAnalytics : returns\nprediction
StreamAnalytics --> CosmosSQL : persists\ntransaction data
StreamAnalytics --> Synapse : persists for\nanalytics
StreamAnalytics --> OrchFunction : triggers on\nfraud event

OrchFunction --> BenfordFunction : invokes for\nstatistical analysis
OrchFunction --> FraudRingFunction : invokes for\nring detection
BenfordFunction --> CosmosSQL : queries\ntransaction patterns
FraudRingFunction --> CosmosGremlin : queries\nrelationship graph
CosmosGremlin --> FraudRingFunction : returns\nfraud rings
CosmosSQL --> BenfordFunction : returns\ntransaction data

AzureML --> MLModel : deploys model
Notebooks --> AzureML : trains/configures
Config --> AzureML : configures

ARMTemplate ..> EventHub : provisions
ARMTemplate ..> StreamAnalytics : provisions
ARMTemplate ..> AzureML : provisions
ARMTemplate ..> OrchFunction : provisions
ARMTemplate ..> CosmosSQL : provisions
ARMTemplate ..> CosmosGremlin : provisions
ARMTemplate ..> Synapse : provisions

StreamAnalytics -[#red,thickness=3]-> MLModel : Real-time\nInference
EventHub -[#red,thickness=3]-> StreamAnalytics : High-throughput\nStream
StreamAnalytics -[#red,thickness=3]-> CosmosSQL : Low-latency\nWrites

legend right
    |= Symbol |= Description |
    | Thick Red Lines | Performance-critical paths |
    | <<Message Broker>> | Event streaming service |
    | <<Stream Processor>> | Real-time analytics |
    | <<ML Platform>> | Machine learning service |
    | <<Azure Function>> | Serverless compute |
    | <<Document Store>> | NoSQL database |
    | <<Graph Database>> | Relationship modeling |
    | <<Data Warehouse>> | Analytics storage |
    | <<IaC>> | Infrastructure as Code |
endlegend

@enduml
